Join @btbounds at @highcascade July 4-10th! There are still a few spots left to go boarding on the Mount Hood glacier, skating at HCSC, and enjoy a ton of awesome off hill and apres activities at this women's-specific adult snowboard camp!

Sing karaoke with @686 and @hibeams! Ride with @nitrosnowboards and @alexisroland! Special surprise dinner and campfire hang with the @burtonsnowboards crew! It's going to be an awesome week!
